Background
----------

- what is version control?
    - resume v1, v2, v2_final
    - formal process
- why version control?
    - rollback changes
    - project history
    - backup our work
- Invented by Linus Torvalds (also created linux) to be a better vcs for linux
  kernel code
- industry standard
- distributed

